supplicate, he would supplicate three times, and when he would ask Allah, he would ask three times. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1794 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25197,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/09\/10\/allah-sent-prophet-gentle-teacher\/","url_meta":{"origin":25588,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Teaching: Allah sent me to be a gentle teacher","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 10, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah did not send me to be harsh or obstinate, rather He sent me to teach and to put at ease.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1478 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/12\/believer-or-merely-muslim\/","url_meta":{"origin":25588,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Or maybe he is merely a Muslim?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was distributing charity, so I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, give it to this man for he is a believer.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cOr merely a Muslim.\u201d I said it three times and the Prophet repeated it three\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26024,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/05\/prophet-suffers-hunger\/","url_meta":{"origin":25588,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hunger: The Prophet suffers from hunger all day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 5, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, spend the entire day suffering from hunger. The Prophet could not find even the worst dates with which to fill his stomach. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2978 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u0645\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e\u062f\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28175,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/prophet-salat-duha-four-rakaat\/","url_meta":{"origin":25588,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Duha: The Prophet prays in forenoon four cycles","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt